description:
#249: On this episode we sit down with Garrett and Nicole McNamara for a him and her aspect episode. Garrett is known for breaking and setting world records by surfing the largest wave ever surfed. Garrett has an incredible story struggle and perseverance, constantly pushing past fear barriers to set new records. Garrett's wife Nicole is a wealth of wellness knowledge and mother with a mission to help those around her. Enjoy this wide ranging conversation with this dynamic couple.
